title: Reindeer Section - Son of Evil Reindeer (2002)
description: &#039;Son Of Evil Reindeer&#039; is the second album from the ever expanding Reindeer Section. Headed by Snow Patrol&#039;s Gary Lightbody, and joined by members of Belle & Sebastian, Mogwai, Arab Strap and The Vaselines, to name but a few, the album continues with the gentle lo-fi indie rock of their debut release. Included are guest appearances from Idlewild&#039;s Roddy Womble and Teenage Fanclub&#039;s Norman Blake.
